  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself trapped in a mysterious communal apartment filled with an eerie and unsettling atmosphere. There's no way out, and your only option is an old elevator with two buttons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walk down the corridor and press the elevator's <strong>red button</strong> if you notice an anomaly—something that shouldn’t be there. Press the <strong>green button</strong> if everything seems normal. Your decisions will determine the outcome:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Correct answers bring you closer to the exit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mistakes send you back to the beginning.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/be38d02177c287aeda59b58b20f1e644.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration and Observation:</strong> Carefully examine the corridor and your surroundings. Anomalies can be hidden anywhere within the corridor.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decision-Making:</strong> Test your attentiveness and intuition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replayability:</strong> Each playthrough surprises you with new combinations of anomalies and challenges. The game features around 30 unique anomalies that won't repeat in a single cycle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Graphics:</strong> Stunning visuals create an atmosphere that is truly immersive and haunting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Authentic Ambiance:</strong> Experience the spirit of an old communal apartment filled with mysteries.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover strange and sometimes humorous anomalies:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/1295de5dce0825b538aa0f8427afae0e.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Anomalies:</strong> A blend of bizarre, funny, and truly creepy phenomena awaits you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A severed head in a pot isn’t the scariest thing you might encounter:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/3946c1e3a54e8114b8168661e56a7181.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Charming Cat:</strong> This fluffy companion might be more than meets the eye.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.poster.avif?t=1746110937\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.webm?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336800/extras/ac55fdafa0c9ce6fe7889a79347aa573.mp4?t=1746110937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can You Escape?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or will you remain trapped in an endless cycle of wrong decisions? It all depends on your attention to detail and intuition.</p>",
